The key fix is changing from storing a borrowed reference (`&Client`) to storing an `Arc<Client>`. When you need to use the client, you clone the `Arc` which gives you another handle to the same underlying connection. This keeps the connection alive as long as the `Arc` in the `OnceCell` exists.

